-- Palestinian Politician al-Salhi Visits China, Hua Says
-- B y   H e n r y   S a n d e r s o n
-- 2012-11-21T07:51:08Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-11-21/palestinian-politician-al-salhi-visits-china-hua-says-correct-.html
(Corrects spelling of Israeli in second paragraph.)  Palestinian People’s Party General
Secretary Bassam al-Salhi will visit  China  tomorrow to discuss
violence in Gaza, Chinese Foreign Ministry spokeswoman Hua
Chunying told a briefing in Beijing today.  “We urge relevant parties, in particular the Israeli side,
to exercise maximum restraint, reach an immediate cease-fire and
avoid escalating tension,” Hua said.  Al-Salhi will visit China until Nov. 24, Hua said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Henry Sanderson in Beijing at 
 hsanderson@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Nicholas Wadhams at 
 nwadhams@bloomberg.net  